snippet.title: WWPYPYD (Arle) - Part 1 - Puyo Puyo Dungeon
snippet.description: Waku Waku Puyo Puyo Dungeon.  I finally figured out how to play this game properly...so I might be able to scurry my way through it, despite the language barrier.
